      "content": "<p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">a. &#39;Product Name&#39;: The name of your product (e.g., &#39;Espresso&#39;, &#39;T-Shirt&#39;).</span></p><p></p><p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">b. &#39;SKU&#39;: A unique code for your product (optional, but recommended for inventory tracking).</span></p><p></p><p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">c. &#39;Category&#39;: Assign the product to a category (e.g., &#39;Coffee&#39;, &#39;Apparel&#39;).</span></p><p></p><p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">d. &#39;Product Tags&#39;:</span><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\"> </strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Add multiple keywords to group the product (e.g., &#39;Western&#39;, &#39;Food&#39;, &#39;Promo Item&#39;).</span></p>",
